ty%20to%20do%20what%20Prime%20Minister%20(Narendra%20Modi)%20called%20for%20-%20to%20be%20inclusive%2C%20decisive%2C%20action-oriented%20and%20ambitious%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20out%20that%20India%20assumes%20presidency%20of%20the%20G20%20when%20its%20own%20economy%20is%20on%20a%20strong%20upward%20trend.%20%26quot%3B...%20at%20a%20time%20when%20India%20has%20accelerated%20its%20pace%20of%20growth.%20India%20is%20the%20fifth%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20and%2C%20in%202027%2C%20will%20be%20the%20third%20largest%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20of%20government%20think-tank%20NITI%20Aayog%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EIndia%20To%20Focus%20On%20Global%20South%20At%20G20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-brings-g20-spotlight-back-on-real-issues-of-global-south-s-jaishankar-4115574%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20G20%20during%20its%20presidency%20will%20be%20on%20the%20Global%20South%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20includes%20poor%20countries%20from%20Africa%2C%20Asia%20and%20South%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20as%20early%20as%20last%20year%2C%20that%20while%20it%20is%20understandable%20that%20some%20of%20this%20focus%20is%20on%20issues%20pertaining%20to%20the%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20this%20could%20not%20obfuscate%20the%20real%20concerns%20and%20pain%20points%20of%20the%20Global%20South.%20He%20said%20there%20were%20countries%20who%20could%20not%20feed%20their%20people%2C%20are%20running%20short%20of%20fuel%20and%20had%20suffered%20over%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692948780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F9b83i31_amitabh-kant-ndtv-650_650x400_25_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fg20-summit-india-amitabh-kant-b20-summit