%20is%20suspicious%20that%20the%20Delhi%20Police%E2%80%99s%20investigating%20officer%20%E2%80%9Cmanipulated%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20and%20filed%20charge%20sheets%20in%20a%20riots%20case%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpredetermined%20and%20mechanical%20manner%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20which%20pertains%20to%20violence%20near%20R.P.%20Public%20School%2C%20one%20Salman%20had%20alleged%20that%20he%20was%20shot%20at%20by%20three%20boys.%20The%20court%20had%20hauled%20police%20for%20clubbing%20this%20case%20with%20that%20of%20a%20riotous%20mob%20because%20the%20accused%20are%20clearly%20mentioned%20as%20three%20boys%20here%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20FIR%20had%20been%20clubbed%20with%20a%20complaint%20by%20two%20people%2C%20Mujahid%20and%20Jameer%2C%20who%20had%20said%20that%20their%20shops%20had%20been%20destroyed%20in%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20the%20investigation%20was%20illegally%20clubbed%20in%20the%20FIR%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpretext%20of%20proximity%20of%20place%20of%20incident.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETime%20and%20again%2C%20various%20courts%20in%20Delhi%20hearing%20the%20riots%20cases%20have%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdelhi-riots-probe-injured-complainant-accused-court%5C%22%3E%20pointed%20to%20shoddy%20investigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Delhi%20police%2C%20highlighting%20various%20oversights%2C%20small%20and%20big.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdelhi-violence-real-conspiracy-episode-1%5C%22%3EVarious%20fact-finding%20teams%20have%20also%20highlighted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20investigation%20remains%20partisan%20and%20has%20ensured%20scholars%20and%20activists%20are%20in%20jail%2C%20while%20a%20large%20section%20of%20those%20who%20incited%20the%20riots%20are%20as%20yet%20not%20brought%20to%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692948382000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads