r%20fate%20is%20intertwined.%20Adani%20Enterprises%20tried%20to%20raise%20funds%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20but%20failed...Modi%20will%20have%20to%20answer%20on%20Adani%20in%20Parliament.%20This%20will%20significantly%20weaken%20Modi's%20stranglehold%20on%20India's%20federal%20govt.%20I%20expect%20a%20democratic%20revival%20in%20India%E2%80%A6I%20could%20be%20foolish%2C%20but%20I%20think%20democracy%20will%20flourish%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20Soros%20saw%20India%20to%20be%20happy%20and%20healthy%20in%20the%20UPA%201%20and%20UPA%202%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20in%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20Hindenburg%20report%20Adani%20stocks%20badly%20tumbled%2C%20a%20political%20storm%20erupted%2C%20opposition%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20forced%20complete%20washout%20of%20winter%20session%20of%20Parliament%2C%20all%20kinds%20of%20allegations%20were%20made%20against%20the%20Modi%20government%20by%20its%20known%20critics%20and%20political%20rivals%2C%20but%20as%20the%20time%20passed%20people%20and%20investors%20saw%20through%20the%20possible%20game%20in%20that%20foreign-originated%20report%2C%20Adani%20stocks%20gained%20upward%20momentum%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20committee%20led%20by%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20AM%20Sapre%20on%20the%20Adani-Hindenburg%20issue%20came%20to%20a%20conclusion%20that%20%26quot%3Bprima%20facie%20no%20regulatory%20failure%20on%20part%20of%20the%20SEBI%20around%20the%20allegation%20of%20price%20manipulation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20Soros'%20wishes%20couldn't%20get%20the%20flight%20path%20trajectory%20he%20wanted.%20There%20is%2C%20thus%2C%20this%20informed%20speculation%20the%20OCCRP%20was%20coming%20out%20with%20%26quot%3BHindenburg%202.0%26quot%3B%20to%20try%20and%20cause%20further%20political%20and%20economic%20upheaval%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20proved%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20that%20they%20time%20their%20report%20with%20some%20important%20events%20in%20India's%20calendar.%20Let's%20see%20why%20the%20current%20timing%20is%20important.%20But%20before%20that%20a%20bit%20of%20backgrounder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20a%20six-member%20expert%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20committee%20stated%20that%20there%20was%20evidence%20of%20a%20build-up%20in%20short%20positions%20on%20Adani%20Group%20stocks%20ahead%20of%20the%20release%20of%20the%20Hindenburg%20report.%20Suspicious%20trading%20was%20observed%20on%20the%20part%20of%20six%20entities.%20Of%20these%2C%20four%20are%20FPIs%2C%20one%20body%20corporate%20and%20one%20individual.%20Some%20news%20reports%20suggest%20that%20on%20further%20investigation%2C%20the%20number%20of%20such%20entities%20have%20gone%20up.%20It%20suggested%20that%20SEBI%20ought%20to%20be%20probing%20such%20actions%20under%20securities%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEBI%20is%20expected%20to%20submit%20its%20report%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Aug.%2029.%20It%20is%20nobody's%20case%20to%20suggest%20that%20the%20higher%20judiciary%20verdict%20can%20be%20influenced%20by%20some%20media%20or%20other%20privately%20funded%20reports%2C%20but%20such%20reports%20do%20create%20a%20negative%20buzz%20and%20give%20some%20additional%20talking%20points%20to%20the%20petitioner's%20lawyers%20in%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20less%20than%20a%20fortnight%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20be%20hosting%20the%20G20%20summit%20meeting%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Raising%20political%20dust%20or%20adverse%20economic%2Fstock%20market%20report%20wouldn't%20be%20in%20the%20best%20interests.%20PM%20Modi%20and%20India%20in%20recent%20years%20have%20gained%20great%20stature%20in%20the%20global%20high%20table.%20India%20through%20its%20hard%20work%20in%20various%20sectors%20is%20trying%20overtime%20to%20go%20higher.%20Modi%20has%20already%20declared%20that%20in%20his%20third%20term%20India%20will%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world.%20That%20surely%20does%20not%20go%20well%20with%20India%20and%20Modi%20baiters%20in%20sections%20of%20supposed%20Western%20influence%20groups.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20INDIA%20block%20is%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Aug.%2031.%20It%20has%20been%20proven%20that%20the%20Opposition%20picks%20up%20anything%20and%20everything%2C%20real%2C%20half-truth%20or%20manufactured%2C%20in%20its%20bid%20to%20target%20the%20Modi%20government.%20The%20Soros%20Open%20society-funded%20Hindenburg%202.0%2C%20if%20it%20comes%2C%20would%20be%20instantly%20used%20as%20ammunition.%20More%20so%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20newly%20formed%20alliance%20is%20showing%20signs%20of%20conflict%20and%20contradiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20worthwhile%20to%20recall%20what%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20had%20said%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20that%20he%20was%20not%20sure%20if%20election%20season%20had%20started%20in%20India%2C%20but%20for%20sure%20it%20had%20started%20in%20New%20York%20and%20London.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%202024%20elections%20has%20moved%20even%20closer.%20Soros%20and%20his%20men%20for%20sure%20are%20working%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Delhi)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692945300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-01%2Flefga968_george-soros-wef-_625x300_24_January_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsoros-backed-occrp-getting-ready-for-a-hit-job-on-india-4328098%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Just%20as%20'India%20on%20the%20Moon'%20celebrations%20were%20in%20full%20throttle%20in%20the%20country%20and%20congratulatory%20messages%20pouring%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%20on%20a%20milestone%20achieved%20by%20Indian%20scientists%20at%20ISRO.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsoros-backed-occrp-getting-ready-for-a-hit-job-on-india-4328098%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsoros-backed-occrp-getting-ready-for-a-hit-job-on-india-4328098%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsoros-backed-occrp-getting-ready-for-a-hit-job-on-india-4328098%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-UP%20Minister%20Jailed%20For%20Poet's%20Murder%20To%20Be%20Freed.%20What%20Was%20The%20Case%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20refused%20to%20stay%20the%20release%20of%20former%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20minister%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%2C%20who%20was%20convicted%20in%20the%20sensational%202003%20murder%20of%20poet%20Madhumita%20Shukla%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhumita-shukla-murder-case-ex-up-minister-amarmani-tripathi-accused-of-murdering-poetess-to-be-released-from-jail-4327683%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20to%20be%20released%20from%20jail%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Tripathi%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20also%20to%20be%20released%2C%20have%20been%20serving%20a%20life%20term%20since%202007%20but%20will%20be%20freed%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20'good%20conduct'%20in%20prison%2C%20the%20UP%20government%20said%20in%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shukla's%20sister%20had%20appealed%20the%20release%20of%20Tripathi%20and%20his%20wife.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20while%20declining%20to%20interfere%20in%20Tripathi's%20release%2C%20has%20sought%20a%20reply%20from%20the%20UP%20government%20in%20eight%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUP%20Prisons%20Minister%20Dharamveer%20Prajapati%20had%20earlier%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSuch%20releases%20happen%20on%20basis%20of%20how%20prisoners%20conduct%20themselves%20in%20jail.%20Files%20are%20moved%20and%20acted%20upon%20only%20after%20orders%20from%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20(Yogi%20Adityanath)%20and%20Governor%20(Anandiben%20Patel).%20This%20is%20how%20things%20are%20progressing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20a%20minister%20in%20Mayawati's%20government%2C%20Tripathi%20was%20seen%20as%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20boss'%20right-hand%20man%20and%20had%20initially%20claimed%20he%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20gruesome%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20denials%20were%20up-ended%2C%20though%2C%20after%20a%20DNA%20test%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20indicated%20the%20child%20Ms%20Shukla%20was%20carrying%20when%20she%20was%20shot%20dead%20was%20his.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EMs%20Shukla's%20Family%2C%20Others%20Respond%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shukla's%20sister%20has%20refused%20to%20comment%20on%20Tripathi's%20release%20beyond%20stating%20the%20Governor%20must%20have%20%26quot%3Btaken%20a%20call%20based%20on%20government%20files%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BCannot%20comment%20on%20the%20Governor's%20decision%20but%20I%20can%20say%20that%20the%20Governor%20takes%20a%20call%20based%20on%20government%20files%20and%20does%20so%20after%20deep%20contemplation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20has%20also%20questioned%20Tripathi's%20release%20and%20has%20mocked%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20claiming%20he%20is%20being%20released%20as%20the%20BJP%20%26quot%3Bneeds%26quot%3B%20him%20for%20next%20year's%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*Under%20what%20rules%20are%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%20and%20his%20wife%20being%20released%3F%20It%20seems%20BJP's%20Yogi%20-%20Modi%20model%20has%20become%20stale%2C%20so%20they%20need%20Amarmani.%20They%20may%20even%20end%20up%20needing%20Mukhtar%20Ansari.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20am%20sure%2C%20whichever%20criminal%20in%20jail%20BJP%20needs%20for%202024%20election%2C%20all%20will%20be%20bailed%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20SP%20spokesperson%20Manoj%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20Was%20The%20Madhumita%20Shukla%20Murder%20Case%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhumita%20Shukla%2C%20a%20fiery%20poet%2C%20was%20murdered%20on%20May%209%2C%202003.%20Her%20body%20was%20found%20at%20her%20home%20in%20Lucknow's%20Nishatganj%20area.%20Ms%20Shukla%20was%2024%20years%20old%20and%20allegedly%20Tripathi's%20lover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Famarmani-tripathi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmarmani%20Tripathi%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20then%20a%20four-time%20MLA%20with%20links%20to%20various%20political%20parties%20and%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20influence%2C%20which%20was%20why%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20transferred%20the%20case%20from%20Lucknow%20to%20Dehradun%20after%20Ms%20Shukla's%20family%20feared%20Tripathi%20may%20interfere%20with%20the%20judicial%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shukla%20was%20pregnant%20when%20she%20died%20and%20the%20father%20was%20said%20to%20be%20Tripathi%2C%20something%20confirmed%20after%20forensics%20examinations%20by%20the%20CBI.%20However%2C%20such%20was%20Tripathi's%20unsavoury%20influence%20then%20that%20few%20dared%20speak%20against%20him%2C%20never%20mind%20make%20such%20serious%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22taof97og%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Ftaof97og_amarmani-tripathi_625x300_25_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEx-UP%20minister%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%20had%20denied%20any%20connection%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Madhumita%20Shukla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20in%20October%202007%2C%20Ms%20Shukla's%20sister%20seemed%20to%20emphasise%20the%20fear%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%20evoked%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20not%20an%20ordinary%20person.%20That%20is%20all%20I%20can%20say.%26quot%3B%20When%20asked%20if%20she%20was%20scared%20of%20Tripathi%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20say%20anything%20else%20about%20the%20case%20at%20this%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shukla's%20sister%20also%20spoke%20of%20%26quot%3Bnever-ending%26quot%3B%20threats%20against%20the%20family%2C%20stating%20these%20continued%20even%20after%20the%20case%20was%20transferred%20out%20of%20UP%20and%20to%20neighbouring%20Uttarakhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Tripathi%2C%20also%20speaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20insisted%20he%20was%20innocent.%20%26quot%3BMy%20family%20and%20I%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20this%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHow%20Did%20The%20Investigation%20Play%20Out%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP%20chief%20initially%20ordered%20an%20inquiry%20by%20the%20police's%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Department%20but%20after%20an%20appeal%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fmadhumita-shukla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMadhumita%20Shukla%3C%2Fa%3E's%20mother%20the%20case%20was%20handed%20to%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20she%20(Mayawati)%20rang%20up.%20My%20mother%20said%2C%20'If%20you%20put%20the%20CBI%20on%20the%20case%2C%20the%20truth%20will%20come%20out.%20She%20said%2C%20'OK.%20I%20will%20think%20about%20it'%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Shukla's%20sister%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20was%20finally%20called%20in%20and%20arrested%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%20in%20September%202003.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20released%20on%20bail%20by%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20just%20seven%20months%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%20searching%20for%20justice%2C%20Madhumita%20Shukla's%20family%20then%20went%20public%20with%20their%20allegations%20and%20appealed%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20transferred%20the%20case%20to%20Dehradun%20and%20ordered%20daily%20hearings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20over%20in%20less%20than%20six%20months.%20The%20prosecution%20produced%2079%20witnesses%2C%20of%20whom%2012%20recanted%20testimonies%2C%20while%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%20produced%20just%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Verdict%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmarmani%20Tripathi%2C%20his%20wife%20Madhumani%20and%20two%20others%20-%20Rohit%20Chaturvedi%20and%20Santosh%20Kumar%20Rai%20-%20were%20convicted%20and%20sentenced%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20by%20a%20Dehradun%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhumita-shukla-murder-high-court-upholds-life-term-of-former-mla-amarmani-tripathi-wife-492798%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFive%20years%20later%20the%20Uttarakhand%20High%20Court%20upheld%20the%20sentence%3C%2Fa%3E%20given%20to%20all%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692945240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fi46s9i2_madhumita-shukla_625x300_25_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhumita-shukla-murder-case-amarmani-tripathi-wife-released-from-up-jail-for-good-conduct-4327888%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amarmani%20Tripathi%2C%20a%20former%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20minister%20convicted%20of%20conspiracy%20in%20the%202003%20murder%20of%20poet%20Madhumita%20Shukla%2C%20will%20be%20released%20from%20jail.%20Tripathi%20was%20then%20a%20minister%20in%20BSP%20chief%20Mayawati's%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhumita-shukla-murder-case-amarmani-tripathi-wife-released-from-up-jail-for-good-conduct-4327888%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhumita-shukla-murder-case-amarmani-tripathi-wife-released-from-up-jail-for-good-conduct-4327888%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhumita-shukla-murder-case-amarmani-tripathi-wife-released-from-up-jail-for-good-conduct-4327888%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Average%20salary%20hikes%20for%20job%20switch%20half%20for%20IT%20sector%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692945206000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103048548%2Cimgsize-17930.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Faverage-salary-hikes-for-job-switch-half-for-it-sector-as-hot-skills-dont-attract-a-big-premium-anymore%2Farticleshow%2F103048334.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20once%20notable%20average%20salary%20growth%20has%20come%20down%20from%20the%20range%20of%2050-100%25%20to%20a%20more%20modest%2035-40%25%20for%20%E2%80%9Chot%20skill%E2%80%9D%20sets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Faverage-salary-hikes-for-job-switch-half-for-it-sector-as-hot-skills-dont-attract-a-big-premium-anymore%2Farticleshow%2F103048334.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Does%20Today's%20India%20Need%20'Decolonisation'%20Speak%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24135018%2FF3ZJcv4aoAEfWJn.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20landmark%20essay%20explaining%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20radical%20transition%20from%20Mughal%20rule%20to%20British%20colonialism%2C%20the%20anthropologist-historian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fbooks%2Finvention-of-tradition%2FB9973971357795DC86BE856F321C34B3%5C%22%3EBernard%20Cohn%3C%2Fa%3E%20vividly%20portrays%20how%20a%20significant%20shift%20in%20the%20existing%20socio-symbolic%20order%20was%20brought%20about%20by%20maintaining%20continuity%20at%20the%20level%20of%20courtly%20rituals%20and%20practices.%20In%20pre-colonial%20India%2C%20imperial%20subjects%20high%20enough%20in%20rank%20and%20status%20were%20symbolically%20incorporated%20into%20bodies%20of%20Mughal%20sovereigns%20and%20other%20native%20rulers%20through%20reciprocal%20acts%20of%20offering%20%3Cem%3Enazar%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20receiving%20%3Cem%3Ekhelat%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20public%20ceremonies.%20While%20carrying%20on%20with%20the%20show%20of%20royal%20durbars%2C%20this%20human%20economy%20of%20gift%20based%20on%20loyalty%20and%20patronage%20was%20completely%20transformed%20by%20the%20British%20into%20one%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Equid%20pro%20quo%3C%2Fem%3E%20relationship%20of%20bribery%20and%20tribute%2C%20that%20aided%20their%20commercial%20and%20capitalist%20enterprises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20are%20witnessing%20in%20India%20today%20with%20the%20decolonialisation%20talk%20strikingly%20mirrors%20Cohn%E2%80%99s%20assessment%20of%20British%20colonial%20practices%2C%20if%20only%20in%20a%20reverse%20manner.%20To%20avoid%20being%20seen%20as%20disturbing%20prevailing%20social%20relations%20chastened%20by%20their%20experience%20of%201857%2C%20the%20colonisers%20retained%20the%20imaginary%20spectacle%20of%20the%20Mughal%20court%20to%20cover%20up%20the%20fundamental%20break%20that%20they%20had%20instituted%20in%20the%20symbolic%20world.%20Exactly%20the%20opposite%20can%20be%20discerned%20in%20the%20sudden%20noise%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsedition-law-repealed-three-new-bills-tabled-in-parliament-to-replace-criminal-laws%5C%22%3Edecolonising%20law%20codes%3C%2Fa%3E%2076%20years%20after%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence.%20The%20proposed%20exercise%20of%20indigenising%20laws%20%E2%80%93%20insincere%20at%20best%20and%20dangerous%20at%20worst%20%E2%80%93%20would%20only%20bring%20about%20a%20surface-level%20change%20of%20the%20imaginary%20through%20a%20spectacular%20show%20of%20rejecting%20the%20colonial%20inheritance%20while%20harbouring%20no%20aspirations%20for%20freedom%20at%20the%20structural%20and%20systemic%20level%20of%20the%20symbolic%20order%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECriminal%20law%20and%20justice%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20new%20Bills%20were%20recently%20introduced%20in%20Parliament%20by%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20of%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20to%20overhaul%20the%20criminal%20legal%20system%20that%20has%20been%20in%20existence%20since%20the%20colonial%20period.%20Colonial-era%20laws%20including%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%201860%2C%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%2C%201872%20and%20the%20updated%20Criminal%20Procedure%20Code%20of%201973%20are%20set%20to%20be%20repealed%20and%20replaced%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Bill%20and%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20respectively.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-law%2Fthe-bills-in-perspective-8888597%2F%5C%22%3Eexpert%20analysts%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%20have%20suggested%2C%20these%20Bills%2C%20despite%20their%20grand%20posturing%2C%20largely%20keep%20intact%20the%20inherited%20legal%20edifice%20while%20introducing%20minimal%20changes%20to%20undo%20its%20multiple%20crises%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20police%20and%20prison%20reforms%2C%20and%20vaguely%20drafted%20laws%20and%20their%20arbitrary%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20dealing%20a%20blow%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20linguistic%20plurality%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhindi-imposition-modi-govts-nomenclature-for-new-criminal-law-bills-stirs-row%5C%22%3Eprioritising%20Sanskritised%20Hindi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20their%20titles%20also%20misrepresent%20the%20point%20and%20purpose%20of%20these%20laws.%20For%20instance%2C%20by%20translating%20%E2%80%98penal%E2%80%99%20as%20%E2%80%98nyaya%E2%80%99%20which%20is%20commonly%20associated%20with%20justice%20in%20classical%20Hindu%20philosophy%2C%20one%20of%20the%20Bills%20reduces%20the%20latter%20to%20a%20much%20narrower%20concern%20with%20crime%20and%20punishment.%20It%20is%20anybody%E2%80%99s%20guess%20why%20this%20particular%20term%20was%20selected%2C%20but%20in%20their%202019%20election%20manifesto%2C%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20had%20come%20up%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98Nyuntam%20Aay%20Yojana%E2%80%99%2C%20also%20called%20Nyay%2C%20that%20is%20the%20basic%20income%20scheme.%20Although%20not%20adequate%20for%20the%20universalisation%20of%20welfare%2C%20this%20gesture%20was%20at%20least%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20worldwide%20trend%20among%20political%20theorists%20to%20think%20about%20justice%20through%20the%20question%20of%20social%20redistribution.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20takes%20a%20step%20back%20in%20robbing%20justice%20of%20its%20redistributive%20thrust%20and%20equating%20it%20with%20the%20corrective%20problem%20of%20maintaining%20law%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUCC%20and%20social%20difference%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelative%20to%20this%20new%20development%20in%20the%20field%20of%20criminal%20law%2C%20a%20longstanding%20pet%20project%20of%20the%20BJP%20which%20it%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20actualise%20thus%20far%20is%20the%20elimination%20of%20religion-based%20personal%20family%20laws%20and%20the%20enactment%20of%20a%20uniform%20civil%20code%20(UCC)%20applicable%20to%20all%20citizens%20throughout%20the%20country.%20Undoubtedly%2C%20the%20normative%20pluralism%20of%20state%20and%20non-state%20laws%20on%20issues%20of%20marriage%2C%20divorce%20and%20inheritance%20as%20we%20know%20it%20today%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Funiform-civil-code-needed-to-decolonise-indian-family-law%2Farticleshow%2F102784639.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ecolonial%20product%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20far%20from%20being%20an%20exposition%20of%20the%20much-reviled%20policy%20of%20%E2%80%98divide%20and%20rule%E2%80%99%2C%20legal%20pluralism%20was%20initially%20in%20the%2018th%20century%20driven%20by%20Indophilia%2C%20and%20subsequently%20since%20the%20Queen%E2%80%99s%20Proclamation%20of%201858%2C%20by%20a%20sheer%20strategic%20necessity%20to%20maintain%20imperial%20dominion%20through%20the%20preservation%20of%20social%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20British%20motivation%20may%20have%20been%20with%20regard%20to%20respecting%20India%E2%80%99s%20heterogenous%20social%20life%2C%20anti-colonial%20thinkers%20had%20for%20the%20longest%20time%20separated%20their%20trenchant%20attack%20on%20the%20colonial%20administrative%20apparatus%20from%20a%20more%20affirmative%20orientation%20towards%20the%20empire%20as%20a%20political%20form.%20This%20is%20because%20unlike%20a%20European-style%20nation-state%2C%20an%20empire%20could%20conceptually%20hold%20together%20religious%20and%20cultural%20differences%20without%20erasing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20only%20in%201929%20that%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20adopted%20the%20famous%20Lahore%20resolution%20for%20%3Cem%3Epurna%20swaraj%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20complete%20independence%2C%20as%20the%20nationalists%20finally%20understood%20that%20India%20had%20no%20future%20in%20an%20empire%20which%20could%20not%20serve%20as%20an%20effective%20counterweight%20to%20colonial%20exploitation.%20Yet%2C%20even%20when%20British%20rule%20gave%20way%20to%20a%20new%20nation-state%2C%20there%20remained%20a%20deep%20intellectual%20investment%20in%20ancient%20and%20medieval%20imperial%20figures%20such%20as%20Ashoka%20and%20Akbar%2C%20who%20were%20resurrected%20through%20the%20adoption%20of%20iconographic%20motifs%20and%20history%20writing.%20Although%20nationalism%20inevitably%20had%20a%20homogenising%20influence%2C%20the%20celebrated%20idea%20of%20India%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20%E2%80%98unity%20in%20diversity%E2%80%99%20drawn%20from%20the%20imperial%20past%20sought%20to%20keep%20open%20some%20of%20its%20closures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22How%20Consultative%20Was%20the%20Framing%20of%20the%20Three%20Criminal%20Law%20Bills%2C%20Really%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-consultative-was-the-framing-of-the-three-criminal-law-bills-really%5C%22%3EHow%20Consultative%20Was%20the%20Framing%20of%20the%20Three%20Criminal%20Law%20Bills%2C%20Really%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20UCC%20is%20ever%20brought%20into%20force%20in%20all%20sincerity%2C%20it%20certainly%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20nationalise%20India%E2%80%99s%20legal%20landscape%20which%20would%20then%20be%20disconnected%20altogether%20from%20the%20long%20imperial%20history%20of%20accommodating%20religious%20and%20cultural%20pluralism.%20Without%20in%20any%20way%20giving%20a%20pass%20to%20personal%20laws%20which%20perpetuate%20discriminatory%20practices%20against%20women%2C%20it%20must%20however%20be%20emphasised%20as%20has%20amply%20been%20done%20in%20feminist%20scholarship%20and%20activism%2C%20that%20legal%20uniformity%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fbjp-ucc-with-gender-justice-discrimination-personal-laws%5C%22%3Enot%20the%20same%20as%20gender%20justice%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProgressive%20decolonisation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20movement%20of%20decolonisation%20stemmed%20from%20an%20ardently%20progressive%20impulse%20to%20compel%20European%20empires%20to%20reckon%20with%20their%20violent%20histories%20of%20slavery%20and%20racism%20that%20continue%20to%20mar%20previously%20colonised%20societies%20even%20today.%20But%20in%20India%2C%20the%20decoloniality%20discourse%20has%20been%20appropriated%20by%20Hindu%20nationalism%20which%20extends%20it%20back%20to%20the%20800%20years%20of%20Muslim%20imperial%20rule%2C%20with%20an%20intensely%20parochial%20and%20superficial%20programme%20of%20indigenisation.%20Those%20committed%20to%20a%20forward-looking%20left-liberal%20politics%20must%20pause%20and%20wonder%20whether%20deploying%20this%20language%20which%20has%20been%20entirely%20co-opted%20by%20their%20ideological%20antagonists%20can%20at%20all%20serve%20any%20emancipatory%20purpose%20in%20the%20current%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20decolonisation%20so%20attractive%20to%20Hindutva%20is%20its%20negative%20and%20reactionary%20side%2C%20which%20enables%20enjoyment%20simply%20from%20demolition%20and%20destruction%20of%20all%20kinds%20%E2%80%93%20from%20architecture%20to%20law%20codes.%20This%20is%20a%20complete%20repudiation%20of%20the%20legacy%20of%20modern%20India%E2%80%99s%20founders%2C%20whose%20anticolonial%20politics%20was%20always%20supplemented%20by%20a%20more%20positive%20world-making%20imagination%20directed%20towards%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDemocracy%20and%20the%20foreign%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20times%2C%20the%20key%20marker%20of%20nationalism%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20rejection%20of%20everything%20that%20is%20foreign%20including%20the%20English%20language%20and%20even%20the%20Constitution%2C%20much%20of%20which%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fopinion%2Fonline-views%2Ftheres-a-case-for-we-the-people-to-embrace-a-new-constitution-11692021963182.html%5C%22%3Eapparently%20derived%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20Act%201935.%20One%20way%20to%20respond%20would%20of%20course%20be%20to%20argue%20that%20Indians%20have%20owned%20up%20to%20English%20and%20the%20Constitution%20despite%20the%20colonial%20origins%20through%20continuous%20usage%20and%20customisation.%20But%2C%20more%20fundamentally%2C%20as%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20thinkers%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpress.princeton.edu%2Fbooks%2Fpaperback%2F9780691114767%2Fdemocracy-and-the-foreigner%5C%22%3ERousseau%20to%20Freud%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20indicated%2C%20a%20degree%20of%20foreignness%20is%20elemental%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20democratic%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20decolonial%20posturing%20is%20to%20nativise%20the%20legal%20system%2C%20the%20hidden%20impulse%20driving%20this%20project%20is%20to%20do%20away%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20society%20governed%20by%20law.%20Instead%2C%20what%20takes%20its%20place%20is%20the%20superegoic%20pressure%20of%20collective%20conscience%20and%20majoritarian%20justice.%20Lost%20in%20the%20debate%20about%20the%20British%20or%20Indian%20origins%20of%20our%20legal%20codes%2C%20is%20the%20law%E2%80%99s%20inherently%20alienating%20capacity.%20Law%20forces%20people%20out%20of%20their%20immediate%20context%20of%20family%20and%20kinship%2C%20and%20enables%20them%20to%20forge%20a%20life%20in%20common%20with%20non-identical%20others.%20Even%20in%20this%20distressing%20period%20for%20the%20republic%2C%20we%20must%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20defy%20the%20nativist%20urge%2C%20as%20it%20is%20only%20through%20some%20kind%20of%20self-alienation%20that%20Indians%20can%20form%20a%20real%20political%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDr%20Moiz%20Tundawala%20is%20an%20Associate%20Professor%20of%20Law%20at%20Jindal%20Global%20Law%20School%2C%20Delhi%20NCR%2C%20India%20and%20Dr%20Salmoli%20Choudhuri%20is%20an%20Assistant%20Professor%20of%20Law%20at%20National%20Law%20School%20of%20India%20University%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692945041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24135018%2FF3ZJcv4aoAEfWJn.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdoes-todays-india-need-decolonisation-speak%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20proposed%20exercise%20of%20indigenising%20criminal%20laws%20%E2%80%93%20insincere%20at%20best%20and%20dangerous%20at%20worst%20%E2%80%93%20would%20only%20bring%20about%20a%20surface-level%20change%20of%20the%20imaginary%20through%20a%20spectacular%20show%20of%20rejecting%20the%20colonial%20inheritance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdoes-todays-india-need-decolonisation-speak%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWorld%20Has%20To%20Grow%20With%20Equity%2C%20Inclusiveness%26quot%3B%3A%20G20%20Sherpa%20Amitabh%20Kant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publishe