20months%20after%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20leader%20Ajit%20Pawar%20took%20oath%20as%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Maharashtra%20following%20a%20mutiny%2C%20the%20party's%20patriarch%20Sharad%20Pawar%20today%20denied%20reports%20of%20a%20split%20within%20NCP%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar%2C%2063%2C%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20the%20second%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Maharashtra%20after%20months%20of%20speculation%20about%20his%20possible%20defection%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20along%20with%20eight%20other%20leaders%20who%20followed%20him%20to%20join%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena-BJP%20government%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%2C%2082%2C%20said%20although%20a%20few%20NCP%20leaders%20have%20left%20the%20party%20to%20take%20a%20different%20political%20stance%2C%20this%20does%20not%20constitute%20a%20split.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20majority%20of%20the%20people%20from%20the%20party%20are%20going%20out.%20Some%20people%20have%20taken%20a%20different%20stand%2C%20democracy%20allows%20them%20to%20do%20so.%20It's%20not%20a%20split%20in%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupriya%20Sule%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20daughter%20and%20NCP's%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Baramati%2C%20reiterated%20her%20father's%20remarks%20saying%20that%20the%20party%20is%20united%20and%20that%20there%20is%20no%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20president%20is%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20our%20state%20president%20is%20Jayant%20Patil.%20That%20is%20the%20status%20of%20our%20party%20at%20the%20moment%20and%20we%20stand%20by%20it.%20Our%20party%20is%20not%20in%20an%20alliance%20in%20any%20form%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Some%20of%20our%20people%20took%20a%20different%20stand%20and%20as%20per%20the%20process%20we%20have%20shared%20our%20views%20and%20inputs%20on%20the%20same%20with%20the%20speaker%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sule%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20he%20(Ajit%20Pawar)%20has%20taken%20a%20stand%20that%20is%20against%20the%20party%2C%20and%20we%20have%20given%20a%20complaint%20to%20the%20assembly%20speaker%20and%20are%20awaiting%20his%20response%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20without%20naming%20his%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20those%20who%20rebelled%20against%20the%20party%20by%20saying%20that%20some%20of%20its%20members%20had%20left%20after%20the%20central%20government%20launched%20an%20inquiry%20against%20them%20through%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanners%20were%20put%20up%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20faction%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Beed%20this%20month%2C%20welcoming%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20requesting%20him%20to%20%26quot%3Bbless%26quot%3B%20his%20politically%20estranged%20nephew.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCP%20banners%20carrying%20pictures%20of%20both%20the%20Pawars%20were%20put%20up%20across%20Beed%20hours%20before%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20rally%20in%20Parli.%20This%20came%20against%20a%20backdrop%20of%20a%20war%20of%20words%20between%20the%20NCP%20faction%20led%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20other%20parties%20of%20the%20state%20opposition%20grouping%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%2C%20which%20also%20includes%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20over%20a%20%26quot%3Bsecret%26quot%3B%20meeting%20that%20took%20place%20between%20the%20two%20Pawars%20at%20businessman%20Atul%20Chordiya's%20residence%20in%20Pune%20on%20August%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692942240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ftkiqq69_sharad-pawar-ajit-pawar-ani-650_650x400_05_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fncp-ajit-pawar-sharad-pawar-as-ncp-factions-fight-sharad-pawar-says-no-split-just-democracy-4327970%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nearly%20two%20months%20after%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20leader%20Ajit%20Pawar%20too