olina%20Governor%20Nikki%20Haley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Trump's%20absence%2C%20Ramaswamy%20drives%20the%20GOP%20debate%2C%26quot%3B%20popular%20Axis%20reported.%20The%20first%20poll%20that%20came%20out%20after%20the%20debate%20said%20that%2028%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20504%20respondents%20said%20that%20Ramaswamy%20performed%20the%20best.%20He%20was%20followed%20by%20Florida%20Governor%20Ron%20DeSantis%20with%2027%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20Pence%20(13%25).%20Haley%20received%20the%20vote%20of%20seven%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Fox%20News%2C%20Ramaswamy%20was%20the%20most%20Google-searched%20GOP%20candidate%20for%20the%20first%20Republican%20presidential%20debate.%20He%20was%20followed%20by%20fellow%20Indian-American%20Haley.%20Both%20the%20Indian-Americans%20were%20standing%20next%20to%20each%20other%20on%20the%20debate%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVivek%20Ramaswamy%20Grabs%20Spotlight%20at%20First%20Republican%20Primary%20Debate%2C%26quot%3B%20reported%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%20Its%20editorial%20board%20in%20its%20editorial%20was%20critical%20of%20his%20foreign%20policy%20proposals%20and%20said%20this%20will%20not%20get%20him%20to%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVivek%20Ramaswamy%2C%20the%2038-year-old%20political%20novice%2C%20grabbed%20the%20spotlight%20at%20Wednesday's%20prime-time%20GOP%20presidential%20debate%2C%20but%20there%20was%20little%20sign%20he%20or%20any%20other%20contender%20had%20found%20a%20new%20strategy%20for%20overtaking%20front-runner%20Donald%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20financial%20daily%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20unchecked%20confidence%20and%20insults%2C%20the%20biotech%20entrepreneur%20baited%20his%20rivals%20into%20skirmishes%20that%20dominated%20Republicans%20first%20debate%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%20%26quot%3BHe%20came%20in%20hot%2C%20slamming%20his%20rivals%2C%20smiling%20wide%20and%20showing%20little%20deference%20to%20the%20more%20experienced%20candidates%20on%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20daily%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NBC%20news%20described%20the%20first%20debate%20as%20%26quot%3BVivek%20Ramaswamy%20Show%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20our%20top%20takeaway%20from%20last%20night's%20first%20GOP%20presidential%20debate%2C%20where%20the%20political%20newcomer%20Ramaswamy%20seized%20the%20mantle%20as%20Donald%20Trump's%20defender%20-%20but%20also%20bore%20the%20brunt%20of%20attacks%20from%20rivals%20on%20his%20inexperience%20and%20foreign-policy%20positions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20news%20channel%20reported.%20According%20to%20it%2C%20Mr%20Ramaswamy%20was%20attacked%2011%20times%20by%20his%20rivals%20during%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Messenger%20-%20a%20fast%20growing%20online%20news%20portal%20-%20the%20debate%20resulted%20in%20the%20rise%20of%20Mr%20Ramaswamy's%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVivek%20Ramaswamy%20sparred%20with%20Mike%20Pence.%20He%20battled%20Chris%20Christie.%20And%20he%20picked%20a%20fight%20with%20Nikki%20Haley.%20The%20longshot%20candidate%20and%20entrepreneur%20dominated%20the%20debate%20stage%20on%20Wednesday%20night%2C%20using%20his%20outlier%20policy%20views%20to%20grab%20attention%20and%20stoke%20the%20outrage%20of%20his%20opponents.%20Ramaswamy%20also%20gave%20his%20rivals%20an%20opponent%20to%20attack%20without%20alienating%20Trump%20supporters%20or%20elevating%20the%20second-place%20DeSantis%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramaswamy%20appeared%20confident%20after%20the%20debate%20and%20told%20reporters%20that%20soon%20only%20two%20candidates%20would%20be%20left%20in%20the%20race%2C%20him%20and%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%20On%20the%20debate%20stage%2C%20he%20described%20Trump%20as%20one%20the%20best%20presidents%20of%20the%2021st%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20the%20clear%20winner%20of%20the%20night.%20But%20we%20are%20just%20getting%20started.