trial%20court%20against%20all%2058%20persons%3C%2Fa%3E%20accused%20of%20cheating%2C%20including%20G.V.K.%20Reddy%20and%20Sanjay%20Reddy.%20As%20for%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20charges%2C%20the%20agency%20has%20maintained%20radio%20silence%20on%20the%20matter%20since%20the%20end%20of%20July%202020%20and%20there%20has%20been%20no%20development%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24192029%2FMumbai_03-2016_114_Airport_international_terminal_interior.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24192029%2FMumbai_03-2016_114_Airport_international_terminal_interior.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24192029%2FMumbai_03-2016_114_Airport_international_terminal_interior-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24192029%2FMumbai_03-2016_114_Airport_international_terminal_interior-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669658%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20International%20Airport%2C%20Mumbai.%20Photo%3A%20A.Savin%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20FAL%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20this%20visible%20overlap%20between%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20takeover%20talks%20for%20Mumbai%20airport%20and%20the%20investigative%20agency%20raids%20was%20a%C2%A0%20first%20for%20India%20Inc%2C%20market%20regulators%20and%20Indian%20newsrooms%20chose%20not%20to%20look%20into%20whether%20these%20developments%20were%20linked%20or%20unconnected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20accused%20the%20government%20of%20arm-twisting%20the%20GVK%20group%20into%20selling%20MIAL%20to%20Adani%2C%20GVK%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbhaskarlive.in%2Fgvks-v-sanjay-reddy-rejects-rahul-gandhis-allegations-on-adani-group-and-mumbai-airport%2F%5C%22%3EV.%20Sanjay%20Reddy%20made%20a%20public%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20denying%20he%20had%20been%20coerced.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20far%20as%20GVK%20is%20concerned%20there%20was%20no%20pressure%20on%20GVK%20either%20from%20Adani%20group%20or%20from%20any%20agencies.%20We%20sold%20%5Bthe%5D%20airport%20due%20to%20our%20own%20commercial%20interest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Similarly%2C%20both%20D.V.S.%20Raju%20and%20Adani%20have%20denied%20the%20state%20government%20played%20any%20role%20in%20the%20Andhra%20port%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20considering%20whether%20Adani%20would%20have%20been%20able%20to%20smoothly%20acquire%20Krishnapatnam%20%E2%80%93%20or%20Gangavaram%20in%20its%20entirety%20%E2%80%93%20if%20the%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20government%20had%20not%20acted%20the%20way%20it%20did.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20these%20two%20ports%2C%20even%20assuming%20the%20state%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20looking%20to%20expressly%20benefit%20anyone%2C%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20Adani%20%E2%80%93%20along%20with%20Aurobindo%20Realty%20%E2%80%93%20was%20the%20biggest%20gainer%20from%20the%20increasingly%20Darwinian%20politics%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20MIAL%2C%20the%20unfortunately%20timed%20crackdown%20on%20GVK%20came%20from%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20law%20enforcement%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(M.%20Rajshekhar%20is%20an%20independent%20reporter%20studying%20corruption%2C%20oligarchy%20and%20the%20political%20economy%20of%20India%3C%2Fi%3E%E2%80%99%3Ci%3Es%20environment.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20author%20of%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FDespite-State-India-Lets-People%2Fdp%2F8194879019%2F%5C%22%3EDespite%20the%20State%3A%20Why%20India%20Lets%20Its%20People%20Down%20and%20How%20They%20Cope%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ci%3EReporting%20for%20this%20project%20was%20supported%20by%20Pulitzer%20Center)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAppendix%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20Response%20to%20The%20Wire%E2%80%99s%20Questionnaire%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThank%20you%20for%20approaching%20us%2C%20please%20find%20herewith%20our%20response%20to%20your%20query%20as%20appended%20%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20allegations%20are%20false%20and%20baseless.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%2C%20despite%20not%20being%20true%2C%20such%20allegations%20are%20being%20rehashed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20decades%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20has%20proven%20its%20expertise%20in%20designing%2C%20building%20and%20managing%20world%20class%20infrastructure%20projects%20that%20bring%20about%20primary%20and%20secondary%20economic%20growth%20and%20also%20employment%20and%20benefits%20to%20the%20community.%20In%20addition%20to%20greenfield%20projects%2C%20the%20Group%20has%20also%20relied%20on%20strategic%20acquisitions%20to%20expand%20its%20business.%20Our%20business%20expansion%20decisions%20emerge%20from%20a%20careful%20evaluation%20of%20the%20state%20of%20the%20potential%20acquisition%2C%20its%20prospects%20for%20growth%20and%20its%20synergies%20with%20our%20existing%20operations%2C%20through%20fair%2C%20transparent%20and%20well-established%20business%20processes.%20These%20are%20business%20transactions%20handled%20professionally%2C%20with%20mutual%20respect%20and%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20these%20allegations%2C%20Mr%20GV%20Sanjay%20Reddy%2C%20Vice-Chairman%20of%20the%20GVK%20Group%2C%20has%20publicly%20stated%20his%20views%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Find01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com%2F%3Furl%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Ftransportation%2Fairlines-%2F-aviation%2Fwe-needed-a-strong-financial-partner-who-could-do-a-deal-qu