avoid%20peak%20demand%20times%20and%20protect%20the%20resiliency%20of%20the%20power%20grid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-vehicles-buses-back-to-school-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692907832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e78353a7adf70019072bcf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-vehicles-buses-back-to-school-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Electric%20buses%20are%20taking%20kids%20to%20school.%20Districts%20from%20Florida%20to%20California%20are%20ditching%20some%20of%20their%20diesel-powered%20buses%20for%20electric%20models.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cboudreau%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Boudreau)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-vehicles-buses-back-to-school-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2285%2C000%20healthcare%20workers%20are%20voting%20to%20authorize%20a%20strike.%20If%20they%20do%2C%20it%20will%20be%20the%20largest%20healthcare%20strike%20the%20nation%20has%20ever%20seen.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225398%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20logo%20on%20top%20of%20a%20medical%20building.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e7a846a7adf70019076340%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Coalition%20of%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20Unions%20represents%2085%2C000%20healthcare%20workers%20in%20seven%20states%20and%20Washington%2C%20DC.%3Cp%3EMike%20Blake%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E85%2C000%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20workers%20are%20voting%20on%20whether%20to%20authorize%20a%20strike.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20the%20Kaiser%20strike%20is%20authorized%2C%20it%20would%20be%20the%20nation's%20largest%20healthcare%20strike%20in%20history.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20strike%20would%20impact%20over%2011%20million%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20users%20across%20seven%20states%20and%20DC.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20this%20summer%20%E2%80%94%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fups-teamsters-union-reach-deal-avoid-strike-contract-pay-2023-7%5C%22%3Ejam-packed%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-unemployment-benefits-union-workers-strike-hollywood-sag-aftra-wga-2023-8%5C%22%3Elabor%20activity%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20turns%20to%20fall%2C%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20healthcare%20workers%20could%20find%20themselves%20on%20the%20picket%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Coalition%20of%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20Unions%20will%20conduct%20a%20strike%20authorization%20vote%20beginning%20August%2026.%20The%20vote%20will%20last%20through%20mid-September%2C%20said%20Dave%20Regan%2C%20president%20of%20the%20SEIU%20United%20Healthcare%20Workers%20West%2C%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20union%20members%20vote%20to%20strike%2C%20the%20Coalition%20of%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20Unions%20could%20walk%20as%20early%20as%20October%201.%20With%2085%2C000%20members%20in%20its%20ranks%2C%20it%20would%20be%20the%20largest%20healthcare%20strike%20in%20the%20country's%20history%2C%20organizers%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unioncoalition.org%2Fhome%2F%5C%22%3ECoalition%20of%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20Unions%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20collection%20of%20healthcare%20worker%20unions%20at%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20facilities%20in%20California%2C%20Colorado%2C%20Oregon%2C%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20Hawaii%2C%20Maryland%2C%20Virginia%2C%20and%20Washington.%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20is%20known%20for%20providing%20its%20patients%20with%20both%20coverage%20plans%20and%20healthcare%20under%20the%20same%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaiser%20Permanente%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhealthy.kaiserpermanente.org%2Flearn%2Fwhat-is-kaiser-permanente%5C%22%3Ehundreds%20of%20facilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20country%20%E2%80%94%20including%2039%20hospitals%20and%20715%20medical%20offices%20%E2%80%94%20serving%20more%20than%2012%20million%20people.%20The%20Coalition%20represents%20workers%20in%2095%25%20of%20these%20facilities%2C%20Regan%20said%2C%20meaning%20more%20than%2011%20million%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20users%20could%20be%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20call%20for%20a%20strike%20authorization%20vote%20comes%20five%20weeks%20before%20their%20contract%20with%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20expires.%20Union%20leaders%20say%20they%20are%20calling%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seiu-uhw.org%2Fkaiser-campaign-updates%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincreased%20staffing%20to%20protect%20patients%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20workers%20alike%2C%20a%20raise%20in%20pay%20differentials%20for%20evening%20and%20night%20shifts%2C%20and%20stability%20for%20remote%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Kaiser%20does%20not%20come%20correct%20in%20the%20next%2045%20days%20or%20so%20before%20the%20expiration%20of%20this%20agreement%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20nationwide%20strike%20and%20that%20will%20be%20something%20that%20is%20avoidable%2C%26quot%3B%20Regan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20a%20tragedy.%20It%20is%20not%20what%20this%20workforce%20wants%20to%20do%2C%20but%20it%20is%20what%20we%20are%20being%20left%20no%20choice%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWayne%20Davis%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Kaiser%20Permanente%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20union%20members%20should%20reject%20the%20call%20to%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20take%20any%20threat%20to%20disrupt%20care%20for%20our%20members%20seriously%20and%20have%20plans%20to%20ensure%20continued%20access%20to%20healthcare%20by%20our%20members%2C%20patients%2C%20and%20the%20communities%20we%20serve%2C%20should%20any%20union%20call%20for%20a%20strike%2C%26quot%3B%20Davis%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnion%20representatives%20said%20they%20understood%20that%20a%20strike%20would%20affect%20patient%20healthcare%20but%20that%20staffing%20issues%20at%20the%20company%20were%20already%20negatively%20affecting%20patients%20%E2%80%94%20and%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20strike%20would%20cause%20delays.%20But%20do%20you%20know%20what%20else%20causes%20delays%20in%20patient%20care%3F%20Not%20having%20the%20staff%20to%20treat%20the%20patients%20waiting%20six%20months%20in%20Colorado%20for%20a%20radiology%20appointment.%20That%20causes%20delays%20in%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20Caroline%20Lucas%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Coalition%2C%20said%20at%20the%20press%20conference.%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20go%20on%20strike%20because%20we%20care%20about%20fixing%20those%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20would%20happen%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20unfair%20labor%20practices%2C%20including%20Kaiser%20Permanente's%20failure%20to%20bargain%20in%20good%20faith%20and%20failure%20to%20provide%20relevant%20information%20as%20required%20by%20law%2C%20Regan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavis%20said%20these%20reports%20are%20%26quot%3Bunfounded.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20remain%20committed%20to%20bargaining%20with%20our%20Coalition%20unions%20in%20good%20faith%20and%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20partnership%2C%26quot%3B%20Davis%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20focus%20our%20energy%20on%20frank%20and%20productive%20discussions%20that%20lead%20to%20an%20agreement%2C%20and%20to%20doing%20our%20part%20to%20ensure%20there%20are%20no%20disruptions%20to%20the%20high-quality%20care%20we%20provide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrganizers%20say%20that%20ever%20since%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20began%2C%20healthcare%20workers%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthcare-worker