20is%20robust.%20A%20number%20of%20parties%20compete%20at%20the%20state%20level.%20Sometimes%20there%20is%20a%20misunderstanding%2C%20things%20are%20said%20and%20there%20are%20back%20and%20forth%20%5Bdisagreements%5D%2C%20but%20this%20is%20nothing%20unusual.%20This%20has%20been%20going%20on%20ever%20since%20coalitions%20and%20alliance%20partners%20have%20been%20created.%20That%20is%20the%20historical%20truth%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anshul%20Avijit%2C%20national%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurmurs%20of%20fissures%20between%20the%20two%20new%20alliance%20partners%20emerged%20after%20Delhi%20Congress%20leader%20Alka%20Lamba%20said%20on%20August%2016%2C%20after%20a%20party%20organisational%20meeting%2C%20that%20the%20Congress%20would%20contest%20all%20seven%20seats%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20in%20the%202024%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20decided%20that%20we%20will%20contest%20on%20all%20seven%20seats.%20Seven%20months%20are%20left%20and%20all%20the%20party%20workers%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20prepare%20for%20all%20seven%20seats%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1691757761972077042%5C%22%3Equoted%20as%20saying%20to%20ANI.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20drew%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1691795677318431178%5C%22%3E%20sharp%20reactions%20from%20AAP%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20said%20that%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20form%20an%20alliance%20in%20Delhi%2C%20then%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20going%20for%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20On%20attending%20INDIA%20alliance%20meeting%2C%20AAP%20spokesperson%20Priyanka%20Kakkar%20says%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6If%20they%20(Congress)%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20form%20an%20alliance%20in%20Delhi%2C%20then%20it%20makes%20no%20sense%20to%20go%20for%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20it%20is%20a%20waste%20of%20time.%20The%20party%E2%80%99s%20top%20leadership%20will%20decide%20whether%20or%20not%20to%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FgLv4mg4dRf%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FgLv4mg4dRf%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1691795677318431178%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20clarifications%20were%20issued%20later%20and%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20and%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20national%20convener%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20announced%20that%20he%20will%20attend%20the%20grouping%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20go%20to%20Mumbai%20and%20will%20let%20you%20know%20whatever%20the%20strategy%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20reporters%20on%20August%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Kejriwal%20and%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Pawan%20Khera%20took%20aim%20at%20each%20other%20after%20the%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Felections%2Fbura-haal-hai-kejriwal-slams-ally-congs-chhattisgarh-govt-for-condition-of-govt-schools-101692439880761.html%5C%22%3Ecriticised%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20condition%20of%20government%20schools%20in%20the%20Congress-ruled%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhy%20go%20to%20Raipur%3F%20Performance%20of%20our%20Chattisgarh%20govt%20will%20be%20compared%20with%20the%20previous%20Raman%20Singh%20govt.%20%3Cbr%3ELet%20us%20choose%20a%20sector%20of%20your%20choice%20and%20co