20saw%20in%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20on%20his%20first%20visit%20in%201927.%20However%2C%20he%20realised%20that%20the%20world%20was%20too%20complex%2C%20and%20man%20had%20too%20many%20facets%2C%20to%20be%20encompassed%20by%20any%20single%20or%20total%20explanation.%20He%20himself%20was%20a%20socialist%20with%20an%20abhorrence%20of%20regimentation%2C%20and%20a%20democrat%20who%20was%20anxious%20to%20reconcile%20his%20faith%20in%20civil%20liberty%20with%20the%20necessity%20of%20mitigating%20economic%20and%20social%20wretchedness.%20His%20struggles%2C%20both%20within%20himself%20and%20with%20the%20outside%20world%2C%20to%20adjust%20such%20seeming%20contradictions%20are%20what%20make%20his%20life%20and%20work%20significant%20and%20fascinating.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIndira%20Gandhi%20also%20once%20described%20her%20father%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgenerous%20and%20gracious%20human%20being.%E2%80%9D%20Indeed%20he%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20book%3Cem%3E%20Selected%20Works%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ESecond%20Series%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Volume%2029%2C%20edited%20by%20H.Y.%20Sharada%20Prasad%20and%20A.K.%20Damodaran%2C%20shows%20what%20a%20%E2%80%98generous%20and%20gracious%20human%20being%E2%80%99%20Nehru%20was.%20The%20editors%20of%20this%20volume%20explain%20in%20their%20editorial%20note%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20present%20volume%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3ESelected%20Works%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%3C%2Fem%3E%20draws%20upon%20the%20period%201%20June%20to%2031%20August%201955%20and%20attempts%20to%20record%20the%20major%20developments%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20domestic%20affairs%20and%20also%20its%20international%20relations.%20The%20involvement%20and%20the%20active%20participation%20in%20decision-making%20at%20all%20levels%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20many%20important%20issues%20gives%20to%20the%20narration%20a%20certain%20personal%20continuity%20reflected%20in%20the%20words%20and%20ideas%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20344px)%2085vw%2C%20344px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22172926%2Fimage-1241.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22344%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22172926%2Fimage-1241.png%20371w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22172926%2Fimage-1241-195x300.png%20195w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669204%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22529%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESelected%20Works%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%3A%20Second%20Series%E2%80%99%2C%20Volume%2029%3A%201%20June%20%E2%80%93%2031%20August%201955%3Cbr%3EEd.%20H.Y.%20Sharada%20Prasad%20and%20A.K.%20Damodaran%3Cbr%3EOUP%20(December%202005)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETwo%20separate%20cases%20are%20of%20permanent%20relevance%2C%20one%20about%20Irfan%20Habib%2C%20who%20later%20on%20became%20a%20distinguished%20historian%20at%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%3B%20and%20the%20second%20is%20a%20delightful%20story%20of%20a%20young%20Farooq%20Abdullah%2C%20who%20had%20just%20been%20admitted%20to%20the%20Medical%20College%20in%20Jaipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhen%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20a%20large%20country%20takes%20time%20off%20from%20affairs%20of%20state%20to%20look%20into%20possible%20cases%20of%20inadequate%20justice%2C%20there%20is%20hope%20for%20democracy.%20As%20far%20as%20Nehru%20was%20concerned%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20always%20the%20fugitive%20chance%20that%20conversations%20from%20peak%20to%20peak%20at%20the%20global%20level%20might%20be%20interrupted%20by%20such%20%E2%80%9Cimpulses%20of%20delight%E2%80%9D%20and%20also%2C%20of%20compassion.%20As%20Wordsworth%20said%2C%20this%20is%20after%20all%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20best%20portion%20of%20a%20good%20man%E2%80%99s%20life%2C%20his%20little%2C%20nameless%2C%20unremembered%20acts%20of%20kindness%20and%20of%20love.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ELet%20us%20examine%20these%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIrfan%20Habib%C2%A0was%20sought%20to%20be%20denied%20a%20government%20scholarship%20because%20of%20his%20links%20with%20leftist%20groups.%20Nehru%20discussed%20the%20question%20thoroughly%2C%20understood%20the%20ideological%20dilemmas%20of%20the%20young%20man%20and%20finally%20came%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20he%20should%20be%20given%20the%20scholarship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20Habib%2C%20%E2%80%9Che%20applied%20for%20a%20government%20scholarship%20to%20study%20abroad%20in%201954-55%2C%20but%20his%20passport%20was%20denied%20by%20the%20government%20of%20India%20because%20of%20his%20connections%20with%20the%20CPI%E2%80%9D.%20He%20wrote%20a%20nasty%20letter%20to%20Nehru%2C%20asking%20him%20that%20in%20future%20whenever%20the%20government%20of%20India%20issues%20an%20advertisement%20for%20any%20scholarship%20there%20should%20be%20a%20caveat%20that%20%E2%80%9CCommunists%20need%20not%20to%20apply.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2FIrfan_Habib.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22872%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2FIrfan_Habib.jpg%20604w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2FIrfan_Habib-300x248.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-72253%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIrfan%20Habib.%20Credit%3A%20Amber%20Habib%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20letter%20created%20a%20furore%20in%20the%20PMO.%20Nehru%20enquired%20about%20this%20episode%20from%20then%20vice-chancellor%20of%20AMU%2C%20Zakir%20Husain.%20On%20Husain%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%20Habib%20was%20asked%20to%20meet%20Prime%20Minister%20Nehru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Fessay-passport-and-liberty-by-a-g-noorani%2Farticle34455454.ece%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20renowned%20author%20and%20jurist%3C%2Fa%3E%20A.G.%20Noorani%2C%20Nehru%20met%20Habib.%20Note%20that%20he%20was%20not%20applying%20for%20a%20job%20in%20the%20government%20but%20for%20a%20scholarship%20for%20studying%20abroad.%20That%20Nehru%20conceded%20the%20request%20is%2C%20surely%2C%20less%20relevant%20than%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20felt%20impelled%20to%20write%20about%20the%20incident%20on%20August%2012%2C%201955.%20(Nehru%20and%20Zakir%20Husain%2C%20incidentally%2C%20both%20were%20friends%20of%20Prof.%20Mohammed%20Habib%2C%20the%20scholar%E2%80%99s%20father%20and%20himself%20a%20leftist%20and%20a%20brilliant%20historian.)%20What%20Nehru%20wrote%20deserves%20quotation%20in%20extenso%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIrfan%20Habib%20came%20to%20see%20me%20this%20morning%20and%20I%20had%20a%20talk%20with%20him.%20When%20you%20mentioned%20his%20case%20to%20me%2C%20you%20gave%20me%20the%20impression%20that%20while%20he%20was%20a%20young%20man%20of%20leftist%20sympathies%20and%20ideas%2C%20he%20was%20not%20a%20regular%20member%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%E2%80%A6.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20purpose%20of%20giving%20a%20government%20scholarship%20is%20to%20train%20a%20person%20who%20might%20be%20of%20service%20to%20the%20State%20in%20some%20capacity%20or%20other%20in%20the%20future.%20If%20a%20person%20could%20not%20be%20relied%20upon%20to%20serve%20the%20State%20with%20discretion%20and%20integrity%2C%20then%20obviously%20this%20main%20purpose%20would%20not%20be%20served.%20No%20State%20could%20be%20expected%20to%20go%20out%20of%20its%20way%20to%20give%20scholarship%20to%20a%20person%20on%20whom%20it%20could%20not%20rely%20or%20who%20was%20likely%20to%20indulge%20in%20activities%20which%20were%20harmful%20to%20the%20State.%20I%20use%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98State%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20broader%20sense%20and%20not%20as%20applicable%20to%20a%20particular%20government.%20Also%2C%20I%20realise%20that%20it%20is%20rather%20difficult%20to%20draw%20a%20hard%20and%20fast%20line.%20Anyhow%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20question%20of%20differing%20views%2C%20political%20or%20other%2C%20but%20rather%20of%20a%20basic%20faith%20in%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20integrity.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMy%20own%20experience%20of%20communists%20has%20been%20that%20it%20is%20exceedingly%20difficult%20to%20rely%20upon%20their%20word%20or%20on%20their%20basic%20integrity%20in%20this%20sense.%20Their%20loyalty%20to%20their%20party%20overrides%20all%20other%20loyalties%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20they%20are%20often%20prepared%20to%20function%20in%20a%20way%20which%20cannot%20be%20reconciled%20with%20my%20standards%20of%20personal%20behaviour.%20Again%2C%20I%20repeat%20this%20is%20not%20a%20question%20of%20difference%20in%20idea.%20Personally%2C%20I%20have%20had%20no%20animosity%20against%20the%20communists%20at%20all%20but%20I%20have%20come%20to%20feel%20increasingly%20how%20out%20of%20date%20communist%20parties%20in%20non-communist%20countries%20are.%20As%20I%20told%20Irfan%2C%20they%20are%20like%20the%20Jesuits%20belonging%20to%20the%20strict%20order%20and%20not%20over-scrupulous%20in%20their%20dealings%20with%20others%2C%20provided%20they%20carry%20out%20the%20dictates%20of%20that%20order%20to%20whom%20they%20owe%20their%20basic%20loyalty.%20I%20see%20no%20reason%20why%20the%20Government%20should%20go%20out%20of%20its%20way%20to%20offer%20a%20scholarship%20to%20a%20person%20who%20is%20so%20tied%20up%20with%20an%20order%20of%20this%20kind%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20the%20communist%20party%20or%20some%20other.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EI%20recognise%2C%20of%20course%2C%20that%20one%20must%20not%20judge%20young%20people%20too%20strictly%20and%20youthful%20enthusiasm%20must%20not%20be%20ignored%E2%80%A6%20Anyhow%2C%20in%20the%20balance%2C%20I%20feel%20that%20we%20should%20decide%20in%20favour%20of%20Irfan%20Habib%20as%20a%20special%20case.%20My%20main%20reason%20for%20thinking%20so%20is%20that%20he%20is%20a%20young%20man%20of%20intelligence%20and%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20integrity%20and%20both%20these%20qualities%20will%20no%20doubt%20influence%20his%20future%20growth.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarooq%20Abdullah%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%201955%2C%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20in%201955%20had%20been%20admitted%20to%20the%20Medical%20College%20in%20Jaipur%20and%20was%20apparently%20teased%20by%20fellow%20students%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98son%20of%20a%20traitor%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20the%20imprisoned%20Kashmiri%20leader%20Shaikh%20Abdullah%2C%20who%20was%20in%20jail%20for%20charges%20of%20treason%20and%20conspiracy%20against%20the%20state.%20Nehru%20took%20strong%20exception%20to%20this%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20Shri%20Tikaram%20Paliwal%2C%20a%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Nehru%20urged%20him%20to%20take%20an%20interest%20in%20the%20young%20man.%20He%20had%20also%20heard%20that%20Farooq%20had%20been%20asked%20to%20share%20a%20room%20in%20a%20hostel%20near%20a%20cinema%20in%20the%20town.%20The%20prime%20minister%20specifically%20instructed%20his%20colleagues%20to%20see%20to%20it%20that%20he%20is%20allotted%20a%20single%20room%2C%20however%20small%2C%20in%20the%20Medical%20College%E2%80%99s%20own%20hostel%20on%20the%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20Nehru%20wrote%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20writing%20to%20you%20about%20Farooq%20Abdullah%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Shaikh%20Abdullah%20of%20Kashmir.%20I%20understand%20that%20Farooq%20has%20been%20admitted%20to%20the%20Jaipur%20Medical%20College.%20He%20had%20some%20difficulty%20in%20getting%20a%20place%20in%20a%20Medical%20College%2C%20and%20I%20am%20glad%20he%20has%20at%20last%20been%20admitted%20there.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESome%20people%20foolishly%20imagine%20that%20because%20we%20have%20had%20differences%20with%20Shaikh%20Abdullah%2C%20therefore%20we%20are%20not%20favourably%20inclined%20towards%20his%20son%20or%20his%20family.%20This%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20not%20only%20absurd%20but%20is%20just%20the%20reverse%20of%20how%20we%20feel.%20Personally%2C%20because%20Shaikh%20Abdullah%20is%20in%20prison%2C%20I%20feel%20rather%20a%20special%20responsibility%20that%20we%20should%20try%20to%20help%20his%20sons%20and%20family.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFarooq%20saw%20me%20the%20other%20day%20and%2C%20rather%20casually%2C%20he%20mentioned%20that%20some%20of%20the%20students%20of%20the%20Jaipur%20Medical%20College%20had%20referred%20rather%20insultingly%20to%20his%20father%20as%20a%20traitor%20etc.%20I%20was%20sorry%20to%20hear%20this.%20I%20suppose%20one%20cannot%20go%20about%20telling%20boys%20to%20behave%2C%20but%20tactfully%20one%20should%20try%20to%20create%20a%20different%20atmosphere.%20I%20am%20told%20that%20the%20Principal%2C%20(of%20Jaipur%20Medical%20College)%20Kasliwal%2C%20is%20trying%20to%20help%20Farooq.%20That%20is%20good.%20I%20am%20also%20told%20that%20Hiralal%20Shastri%20has%20promised%20to%20take%20some%20interest%20in%20Farooq.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThere%20is%20one%20point%2C%20however%2C%20in%20which%20I%20would%20like%20you%20to%20interest%20yourself%2C%20if%20it%20is%20possible.%20This%20is%20about%20hostel%20accommodation.%20There%20are%2C%20I%20understand%2C%20two%20hostels%20attached%20to%20the%20Jaipur%20Medical%20College%2C%20one%20in%20the%20College%20compound%20itself%20and%20the%20other%20some%20distance%20away%2C%20near%20a%20cinema.%20At%20present%2C%20Farooq%20has%20been%20given%20a%20room%2C%20or%20perhaps%20he%20shares%20a%20room%20in%20the%20hostel%20near%20the%20cinema.%20Normally%2C%20first%20year%20students%20are%20sent%20there.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20all%20the%20circumstances%2C%20however%2C%20it%20would%20be%20better%20for%20him%20to%20be%20given%20accommodation%20in%20the%20hostel%20in%20the%20College%20compound%20itself.%20Also%2C%20that%20if%20possible%20he%20should%20be%20given%20a%20room%20by%20himself%2C%20however%20small%20the%20room%20might%20be.%20Living%20with%20other%20boys%2C%20who%20perhaps%20do%20not%20like%20him%20or%20make%20fun%20of%20him%2C%20would%20create%20difficulties.%20Farooq%20has%20obviously%20gone%20through%20a%20very%20difficult%20period%20during%20the%20last%20two%20years%20and%2C%20at%20his%20age%2C%20there%20is%20danger%20of%20his%20developing%20complexes%20and%20the%20like.%20If%20however%2C%20he%20has%20good%20work%20to%20do%2C%20proper%20living%20quarters%20and%20some%20friendly%20companionship%2C%20this%20would%20have%20a%20very%20good%20effect%20on%20him.%20I%20would%2C%20therefore%2C%20like%20you%20to%20interest%20yourself%20in%20this%20matter%20and%20have%20a%20talk%20with%20Kasliwal%20on%20the%20subject%20and%20see%20what%20can%20be%20done.%20You%20might%20also%20later%20see%20Farooq%20and%20tell%20him%20that%20he%20can%20come%20to%20you%20for%20any%20help.%20Keep%20in%20touch%20with%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThere%20is%20another%20story%20about%20Farooq%20Abdullah%E2%80%99s%20admission%20to%20Jaipur%20Medical%20but%20it%20is%20totally%20off%20the%20record