%20relied%20upon%20to%20serve%20the%20State%20with%20discretion%20and%20integrity%2C%20then%20obviously%20this%20main%20purpose%20would%20not%20be%20served.%20No%20State%20could%20be%20expected%20to%20go%20out%20of%20its%20way%20to%20give%20a%20scholarship%20to%20a%20person%20on%20whom%20it%20could%20not%20rely%20or%20who%20was%20likely%20to%20indulge%20in%20activities%20which%20were%20harmful%20to%20the%20State.%20I%20use%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9CState%E2%80%99%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20broader%20sense%20and%20not%20as%20applicable%20to%20a%20particular%20government.%20Also%2C%20I%20realise%20that%20it%20is%20rather%20difficult%20to%20draw%20a%20hard%20and%20fast%20line.%20Anyhow%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20question%20of%20differing%20views%2C%20political%20or%20other%2C%20but%20rather%20of%20a%20basic%20faith%20in%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20integrity.%20My%20own%20experience%20of%20communists%20has%20been%20that%20it%20is%20exceedingly%20difficult%20to%20rely%20upon%20their%20word%20or%20on%20their%20basic%20integrity%20in%20this%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20loyalty%20to%20their%20party%20overrides%20all%20other%20loyalties%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20they%20are%20prepared%20often%20to%20function%20in%20a%20way%20which%20cannot%20be%20reconciled%20with%20my%20standards%20of%20personal%20behaviour.%20Again%2C%20I%20repeat%20this%20is%20not%20a%20question%20of%20difference%20in%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPersonally%2C%20I%20have%20had%20no%20animosity%20against%20the%20communists%20at%20all%20but%20I%20have%20come%20to%20feel%20increasingly%20how%20quite%20out%20of%20date%20communist%20parties%20in%20non-communist%20countries%20are.%20As%20I%20told%20Irfan%2C%20they%20are%20like%20the%20Jesuits%20belonging%20to%20the%20strict%20order%20and%20not%20over-scrupulous%20in%20their%20dealings%20with%20others%2C%20provided%20they%20carry%20out%20the%20dictates%20of%20that%20order%20to%20whom%20they%20owe%20their%20basic%20loyalty.%20I%20see%20no%20reason%20why%20Government%20should%20go%20out%20of%20its%20way%20to%20offer%20a%20scholarship%20to%20a%20person%20who%20is%20so%20tied%20up%20with%20an%20order%20of%20this%20kind%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20the%20communist%20party%20or%20some%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20recognise%2C%20of%20course%2C%20that%20one%20must%20not%20judge%20young%20people%20too%20strictly%20and%20youthful%20enthusiasm%20must%20not%20be%20ignored.%20Probably%2C%20with%20some%20greater%20experience%2C%20one%20grows%20out%20of%20these%20immature%20grooves%20of%20thought%20and%20action.%20Anyhow%2C%20in%20the%20balance%2C%20I%20feel%20that%20we%20should%20decide%20in%20favour%20of%20Irfan%20Habib%20as%20a%20special%20case.%20My%20main%20reason%20for%20so%20thinking%20is%20that%20he%20is%20a%20young%20man%20of%20intelligence%20and%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20integrity%20and%20both%20these%20qualities%20will%20no%20doubt%20influence%20his%20future%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%2C%20therefore%2C%20advising%20the%20Education%20Ministry%20to%20give%20him%20the%20scholarship.%20Naturally%2C%20his%20future%20behaviour%20will%20be%20a%20consideration%20to%20be%20kept%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYours%20sincerely%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJawaharlal%20Nehru%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandit%20JL%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20letter%20to%20Tikaram%20Paliwal%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20Tikaram%20Paliwal%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%2017%20July%201955%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20dear%20Tikaramji%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20writing%20to%20you%20about%20Farooq%20Abdullah%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Shaikh%20Abdullah%20of%20Kashmir.%20I%20understand%20that%20Farooq%20has%20been%20admitted%20in%20the%20Jaipur%20Medical%20College.%20He%20had%20some%20difficulty%20in%20getting%20a%20place%20in%20a%20Medical%20College%2C%20and%20I%20am%20glad%20he%20has%20at%20last%20been%20admitted%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20foolishly%20imagine%20that%20because%20we%20have%20had%20differences%20with%20Shaikh%20Abdullah%2C%20ther