%2C%20and%20to%20follow%20due%20processes%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692876600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21000804%2FUntitled-design-6.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmedia-bodies-condemn-govts-action-blocking-website-social-media-handles-of-the-kashmir-walla%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%2C%20Indian%20Women%20Press%20Corps%2C%20Press%20Association%2C%20Delhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%2C%20and%20Working%20News%20Cameraman%20Association%20said%20the%20government's%20move%20'raises%20serious%20questions%20about%20the%20state%20of%20press%20freedom'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmedia-bodies-condemn-govts-action-blocking-website-social-media-handles-of-the-kashmir-walla%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Catastrophic%20breeding%20failure'%20of%20emperor%20penguins%20amid%20record%20low%20Antarctic%20sea%20ice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692876540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-antarctica-emperor-penguin_6261296.jpg%3F20230824151843%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fcatastrophic-breeding-failure-of-emperor-penguin-colonies-for-first-time-due-to-record-low-antarctic-sea-ice-12946527%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Emperor%20penguins%20have%20suffered%20their%20first%20%26quot%3Bwidespread%20breeding%20failure%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20record%20low%20Antarctic%20sea%20ice%2C%20reinforcing%20projections%20the%20species%20will%20be%20virtually%20extinct%20by%202100%2C%20scientists%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A288%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fcatastrophic-breeding-failure-of-emperor-penguin-colonies-for-f