IV%2FAIDS%20and%20sexuality.%20That%20is%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20dedicate%20my%20life%20to%20assisting%20persons%20with%20HIV.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-3-1692621159.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Since%20his%20diagnosis%2C%20Gautam%20has%20dedicated%20his%20life%20to%20spreading%20awareness%20of%20the%20disease.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-3-1692621159.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-3-1692621159-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-3-1692621159-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-3-1692621159-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGautam-Yadav-3-1692621159-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327824%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESince%20his%20diagnosis%2C%20Gautam%20has%20dedicated%20his%20life%20to%20spreading%20awareness%20of%20the%20disease.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%2015%20years%2C%20the%2032-year-old%20has%20been%20working%20as%20a%20programme%20officer%20with%20Delhi-based%20non-profit%20India%20HIV%2FAIDS%20Alliance%20with%20PLHIV%20in%20the%20sex%20worker%20and%20transgender%20community%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20who%20struggle%20with%20drug%20addiction.%20Under%20the%20programme%2C%20he%20helps%20them%20overcome%20stigma%20and%20misinformation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20assists%20them%20in%20accessing%20counselling%2C%20getting%20a%20timely%20diagnosis%2C%20and%20referring%