nt.%20Here%2C%20oak%20logs%20are%20deployed%20which%20result%20in%20mushrooms%20having%20a%20better%20taste%20and%20higher%20medicinal%20value%2C%20informs%20Lh%C3%BCvevol%C3%BC.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20started%20her%20journey%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F268725%2Fhow-to-oyster-mushroom-farming-home-cultivation-gujarat-pushpa-patel-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivating%20these%20mushrooms%3C%2Fa%3E%20near%20her%20home%20after%20her%20interaction%20with%20Dr%20Longkumer%2C%20she%20says%20she%20never%20anticipated%20the%20trajectory%20of%20events%20that%20would%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20started%20as%20a%20side%20hobby%2C%20but%20I%20gradually%20began%20seeing%20the%20potential%20behind%20the%20cultivation.%20Seeing%20people%E2%80%99s%20interest%20in%20the%20product%20allowed%20me%20to%20expand%20the%20hobby%20to%20an%20entrepreneurial%20capacity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENative%20Organics%20also%20encourages%20their%20farmers%20to%20grow%20these%20mushrooms%20by%20supplying%20them%20with%20oak%20saplings.%20One%20of%20the%20farmers%20Veshosel%C3%BC%20says%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20aware%20that%20mushrooms%20could%20be%20used%20for%20business.%20%E2%80%9CNative%20Organics%20has%20helped%20marginal%20farmers%20like%20myself%20by%20providing%20market%20linkage%3B%20otherwise%20it%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20sell%20produce%20in%20small%20quantities.%20Income%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F269518%2Fpushpa-jha-mushroom-farming-women-entrepreneur-success-story-bihar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eselling%20shiitake%20mushrooms%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20helps%20us%20in%20managing%20household%20expenses%20during%20seasons.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20for%20Lh%C3%BCvevol%C3%BC%20there%20is%20no%20looking%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C