ments.%20His%20impact%20extends%20far%20beyond%20the%20Indian%20comedy%20circuit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Queer%20Comedian%20from%20Mumbai%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119-300x159.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119-500x264.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119-768x406.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_169502534_271463471131437_1152995525555498624_n_1080-1691803119-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327140%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22571%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20more%20I%20delved%20into%20my%20queer%20self%2C%20the%20more%20I%20realised%20that%20this%20is%20my%20reality%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20out%2C%20Navin%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20really%20fearful%20of%20talking%20about%20his%20sexuality%2C%20and%20credits%20some%20of%20his%20%E2%80%98seniors%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20business%20for%20giving%20out%20useful%20pointers.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20senior%20comics%20%E2%80%94%20Kunal%20Kamra%20and%20Sapan%20Verma%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20would%20advise%20us%20that%20%E2%80%98Maybe%20perfect%20that%20one%20five-minute%20set%E2%80%99.%20In%20the%20open%20mic%20circuit%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20of%20us%20performing%20at%20the%20same%20time%20that%20you%20also%20have%20to%20stand%20out.%20I%20knew%20that%20being%20queer%20on%20a%20given%20lineup%20was%20definitely%20going%20to%20be%20a%20standout%20because%20nobody%20%5Bin%20the%20audience%5D%20knew%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20five-minute%20set%20Navin%20tried%20to%20perfect%20was%20about%20his%20coming%20out%20experiences.%20However%2C%20his%20set%20was%20initially%20not%20doing%20well.%20Paying%20Rs%20300%20to%20just%20travel%20from%20North%20Bombay%20to%20South%20Bombay%20and%20an%20additional%20Rs%20300%20to%20perform%20an%20open%20mic%20set%20at%20the%20Canvas%20Laugh%20Club%20initially%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20like%20a%20worthwhile%20pursuit.%20Naturally%2C%20some%20doubts%20had%20begun%20to%20creep%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAllaying%20my%20doubts%2C%20comics%20like%20Sapan%20and%20Kaneez%20(Surka)%20were%20kind%20enough%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98Maybe%20break%20it%20%5Bbeing%20gay%5D%20down%20for%20straight%20people%E2%80%99%3B%20%E2%80%98Maybe%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20the%20concept%20of%20top%20and%20bottom%20means%E2%80%99%3B%20or%20%E2%80%98They%20%5Bstraight%20people%5D%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20Grindr%20is.%20They%20%5Bstraight%20people%5D%20have%20no%20idea%20about%20queer%20people%20in%20this%20country%20and%20how%20they%20live%2C%20right%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20pointers%20made%20sense.%20My%20first%20idea%20was%20that%20the%205-minute%20set%20has%20to%20become%20a%2010-minute%20one%20because%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20break%20everything%20down%20slowly%2C%20and%20therein%20the%20humour%20came%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20recent%20special%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20see%20Navin%20explaining%20top%20and%20bottom%20%5Bsex%20positions%5D%20to%20people.%20These%20jokes%20are%20the%20outcome%20of%20trialling%20them%20for%20years%20before%20implementing%20them%20in%20real%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20when%20I%20say%20jokes%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98Kerala%20is%20bottom%2C%20Delhi%20is%20top%E2%80%99%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20call%20back%20to%20the%20audience%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20an%20inbuilt%20joke%20as%20well.%20The%20demographic%20of%20the%20country%20also%20is%20very%20vivid%20in%20terms%20of%20sexual%20preferences.%20The%20%E2%80%98top%20and%20bottom%E2%80%99%20joke%20has%20become%20a%20reel%20on%20my%20Instagram%20handle.%20If%20you%20read%20the%20comments%20section%20right%20now%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20full%20of%20gay%20people%20trying%20to%20hook%20up%20with%20each%20other.%20What%20I%20like%20about%20queer%20culture%20is%20that%20we%20somehow%20find%20a%20way%20to%20thrive%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Navin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETaking%20the%20straights%20to%20gay%20school.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMy%20full%20special%20is%20here%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FH9W4FYuVnj%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FH9W4FYuVnj%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FMl5xm3p3OW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FMl5xm3p3OW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Navin%20Noronha%20(%40HouseOfNoronha)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHouseOfNoronha%2Fstatus%2F1673571572509208576%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2027%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20finding%20new%20avenues%20to%20tell%20jokes%2C%20Navin%20has%20over%20the%20span%20of%20his%20career%20found%20a%20way%20to%20completely%20embrace%20his%20lived%20experiences.%20Early%20on%2C%20there%20was%20trepidation%20about%20revealing%20his%20past%20and%20the%20circumstances%20he%20was%20raised%20in.%20He%20didn%E2%80%99t%20tell%20people%20about%20growing